{
  "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "素数，是只能被一和自己整除的数，它们像质点一样构成整数的骨架。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.78,
      "size": 44496,
      "text": "判断一个数是不是素数，通常靠试除。但有没有一个漂亮的公式，一眼道破？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "十八世纪的数学家发现，阶乘竟然藏着素数的秘密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-1",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/theorem-thm-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.15,
      "size": 50400,
      "text": "威尔逊定理说：整数 n 大于一时，n 是素数，当且仅当 n 减一的阶乘除以 n 余 n 减一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-2",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "写成同余就是 n 减一的阶乘 ≡ 负一，模 n。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-3",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "注意这是充要条件，素数满足它，也只有素数满足它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "modfact",
      "line_id": "mod-1",
      "filename": "modfact-mod-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/modfact-mod-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "阶乘增长极快，二十的阶乘就有十九位数，直接算必然溢出。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "modfact",
      "line_id": "mod-2",
      "filename": "modfact-mod-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/modfact-mod-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.79,
      "size": 44640,
      "text": "诀窍是边乘边取模：每乘一个数就对 n 取一次余数，结果始终待在零到 n 之间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "modfact",
      "line_id": "mod-3",
      "filename": "modfact-mod-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/modfact-mod-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "这样即便 n 很大，计算也稳稳当当，不会越界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "contrast",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "contrast-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/contrast-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "看图中的条形：素数处，余数恰好等于 n 减一，绿色条几乎顶到最高。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "contrast",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "contrast-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/contrast-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "合数处却大多塌成零，因为它的因子早已配对相乘，把余数抹平。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "contrast",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "contrast-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/contrast-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "唯一的例外是四，它的余数是二，其余合数都乖乖归零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "拖动滑块选一个 n，看它的余数是不是等于 n 减一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "等式成立就是素数，塌陷为零就是合数，判据一试便知。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "威尔逊定理用一句同余式，精准圈出了所有素数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "取模阶乘让庞大的运算收进小小的余数里，优雅又可算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "wilson-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/wilson-theorem/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "一个阶乘，认出了素数的面孔，数学之美又添一笔，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 39.14,
  "total_size": 626112
}